"><h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading" id=3D"h-what-is-the-volume-of-a-triangular=
-prism">What is the volume of a triangular prism?</h2>



<p></p>



<p>The <strong>volume of a triangular prism</strong> is how much space ther=
e is inside a triangular prism. A triangular prism is a polyhedron (3D shap=
e made from polygons) with two congruent triangular ends connected by three=
 rectangles.</p>



